description: Summarize the results from different performance metrics

panels.description: The average throughput of all benchmarks (except noop) and all terminal values. See **Throughput Trends** for more details.

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",1d),
  (((metrics->>'throughput')::numeric-FIRST_VALUE((metrics->>'throughput')::numeric) OVER(PARTITION BY benchmark_type)) / 
  FIRST_VALUE((metrics->>'throughput')::numeric) OVER(PARTITION BY benchmark_type)) as "ycsb32"
FROM oltpbench_results
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time") AND
  benchmark_type = 'ycsb' AND
  wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
  max_connection_threads = '32' AND
  terminals = '32' AND
  git_branch = 'origin/master'

panels.title: Throughput

panels.description: Latency metrics averaged across all benchmarks (except noop) and all terminal values. See **Latency Trends** for more details.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("time",1d),
  avg((metrics->'latency'->>'avg')::numeric) as "avg",
  avg((metrics->'latency'->>'l_90')::numeric) as "l_90",
  avg((metrics->'latency'->>'l_95')::numeric) as "l_95",
  avg((metrics->'latency'->>'l_99')::numeric) as "l_99",
  git_commit_id
FROM oltpbench_results
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time") AND
  query_mode = 'extended' AND
  benchmark_type != 'noop' AND
  client_time = 60 AND
  git_branch = 'origin/master' AND
  wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
  max_connection_threads = 32
GROUP BY 1, git_commit_id
ORDER BY 1

panels.title: Latency

panels.description: The average throughput for all benchmarks (except noop) and all terminal values. See **Scalability Details** for more details.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
	MAX(time) as time,
	terminals::text as metric,
	AVG(value) as value
FROM (
	SELECT DISTINCT ON (terminals, benchmark_type)
		time,
		benchmark_type,
		terminals,
		CAST(metrics->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION) as value
	FROM oltpbench_results
	WHERE
    $__timeFilter("time") AND
		benchmark_type != 'noop' AND
    client_time = 60 AND
    git_branch = 'origin/master' AND
    wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
    max_connection_threads = 32
	ORDER BY terminals, benchmark_type, time desc
) AS tmp
GROUP BY terminals

panels.title: Throughput by Terminal

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  git_commit_id
FROM oltpbench_results
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time") AND
   benchmark_type = 'tatp' AND
    client_time = 60 AND
    git_branch = 'origin/master' AND
    wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
    max_connection_threads = 32
ORDER BY time ASC

SELECT
	time,
	real_throughput AS "actual throughput", 
	expect_throughput AS "expected throughput",
	real_throughput - expect_throughput AS "difference"
FROM (
	SELECT
		throughput as real_throughput
	FROM (
		SELECT 
			MAX(time) as time,
			terminals as metric,
			AVG(throughput) as throughput
		FROM (
			SELECT DISTINCT ON (terminals, benchmark_type)
				time,
				benchmark_type,
				terminals,
				(metrics->>'throughput')::numeric as throughput
			FROM oltpbench_results
			WHERE
        $__timeFilter("time") AND
				benchmark_type != 'noop' AND
        client_time = 60 AND
        git_branch = 'origin/master' AND
        wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
        max_connection_threads = 32
			ORDER BY terminals, benchmark_type, time desc
		) AS distinct_table
		GROUP BY terminals
	) AS avg_table
	WHERE metric = ${terminals}
) AS real_table 
CROSS JOIN (
	SELECT
		time,
		${terminals}*throughput AS expect_throughput
	FROM (
		SELECT 
			MAX(time) as time,
			terminals as metric,
			AVG(throughput) as throughput
		FROM (
			SELECT DISTINCT ON (terminals, benchmark_type)
				time,
				benchmark_type,
				terminals,
				(metrics->>'throughput')::numeric as throughput
			FROM oltpbench_results
			WHERE

        git_branch = 'origin/master' AND
        wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
        max_connection_threads = 32

		GROUP BY terminals
	) AS avg_table
	WHERE metric = 1
) AS expect;

panels.description: The throughput over the course of the TATP benchmark. Throughput is sampled every 5 seconds.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  NOW()+ CONCAT(incremental.time::text,' second')::interval - '10 minute'::interval as "time",
	TRIM('"' FROM incremental.throughput::text)::numeric as "throughput"
FROM 
  oltpbench_results oltp, LATERAL(
  	SELECT 
    	value->'time' as "time",
    	value->'throughput' as "throughput"
  	FROM 
  	  jsonb_array_elements(oltp.incremental_metrics)
	) incremental
WHERE
	oltp.time = (
		SELECT time
		FROM oltpbench_results
		WHERE
		  query_mode = 'extended' AND
			benchmark_type = 'tatp' AND
			client_time = 600 AND
      git_branch = 'origin/master' AND
      wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
      max_connection_threads = 32
		ORDER BY time DESC
		LIMIT 1
	);

SELECT
  NOW()+ CONCAT(incremental.time::text,' second')::interval - '10 minute'::interval as "time",
	(incremental.latency->>'avg')::numeric as "avg",
	(incremental.latency->>'l_90')::numeric as "l_90",
	(incremental.latency->>'l_95')::numeric as "l_95",
	(incremental.latency->>'l_99')::numeric as "l_99"
FROM 
  oltpbench_results oltp, LATERAL(
  	SELECT 
    	value->'time' as "time",
    	value->'latency' as "latency"
  	FROM 
  	  jsonb_array_elements(oltp.incremental_metrics)
	) incremental
WHERE
	oltp.time = (
		SELECT time
		FROM oltpbench_results
		WHERE
		  query_mode = 'extended' AND
			benchmark_type = 'tatp' AND
			client_time = 600 AND
      git_branch = 'origin/master' AND
      wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
      max_connection_threads = 32
		ORDER BY time DESC
		LIMIT 1
	);
